{"tid":1192554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六條行車線","createTime":"2019-06-08T13:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T16:11:30.000Z","uid":74058,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"537498c4cae2d6637fcfc3c5f9d8cbcdce52361e","tid":1192554,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:09:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2003</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://sparkpost.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsparkpost.files.wordpress.com%2F2013%2F04%2Fc2.jpg&h=58843546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://m.renminbao.com/rmb/article_images/2014/07/04/A8-445-4-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.renminbao.com%2Frmb%2Farticle_images%2F2014%2F07%2F04%2FA8-445-4-1.jpg&h=859b041f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2014</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2018/11/23/442849/wnnp021p01a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2018%2F11%2F23%2F442849%2Fwnnp021p01a.jpg&h=1f45f0fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/bc/29.9.14_Hong_Kong_protest_near_Tamar.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fb%2Fbc%2F29.9.14_Hong_Kong_protest_near_Tamar.jpg&h=98df2f14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8458ffa010905deacee6aa21bd4c4341865ab9b","tid":1192554,"uid":41389,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:10:18.000Z","msg":"-遊行起點：銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）<br />\n-遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n-集合時間：2：30PM<br />\n-起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n-衝定唔衝，自己執生<br />\n-記得宗旨：不散<br />\n<br />\n溫和：<br />\n<strong>【長期置頂】69反送中遊行須知整合</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[懶人包] 第一次參加遊行的常見疑問Q&amp;A</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【極重要】69遊行記得帶防Rfid卡套</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武： <br />\n<strong>食放題須知，全部資料，一世受用</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[law撚］被捕人仕須知</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>［抗爭手冊］End game前準備</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑色三毛警告信號現正生效 6月8日16時</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過70次/禁70次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備時項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待明天遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfe594e954c22713c17b222f1f5c156af95e3d63","tid":1192554,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:10:42.000Z","msg":"6月9號遊行嘅方針:兄弟爬山，各自努力，避免割席，拒絕篤灰，不打飛機，不傳耳語，不搞抹黑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1192414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1192414</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e3cf6f900f20c0570d4cdafa13d0247cb8519915","tid":1192554,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c0e6b0aa28f8fb97dcafdaa9d4a47f297525ee5","tid":1192554,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34e05819160332122c3637a91ca1dbe320ef3e9","tid":1192554,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92bae43776bde79ae7328415c6682af2fe9315b","tid":1192554,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:26:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1c74bad583a7755cd711d63c1a6b12d866f106","tid":1192554,"uid":15482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:28:09.000Z","msg":"人手置頂"},{"pid":"333090ab27c8e81cd8e971be815e46f140f2263e","tid":1192554,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153df2788324b0281e196d6829b3d1daadc2e989","tid":1192554,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20826a6f6cfd809a1660fcf5798654ed9aac7193","tid":1192554,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply